title: Bieber on dad’s awkward penis post
text: Happy Back to the Future day, everyone! 0:30 AM James Hetherington IT’S October 21, 2015 — and that’s a pretty special day for any fans of Back To The Future, the much-loved trilogy of movies starring Michael J. Fox. Bieber on dad’s awkward penis post 0:27 AM Network Writers JUSTIN Bieber has responded to his dad’s awkward tweet boasting about the size of his son’s penis. Khloe ‘splits’ from boyfriend 0:21 AM Network Writers KHLOE Kardashian has reportedly split from NBA star James Harden to support her hospitalised estranged husband, Lamar Odom. The big US role Angus almost missed 0:00 AM Shannon Molloy National TV Writer HAD the Channel Ten drama Party Tricks not been axed, Angus Sampson would’ve missed out on a major US role that looks set to make his career overseas. Limitless actor can’t watch herself 0:00 AM Tiffany Dunk National TV Editor SHE’S been nominated for an Oscar, had a thirty plus year career yet Mary Elizabeth Mastrantonio says she still cringes watching herself on TV. Clive Owen’s bathroom promise to wife 0:00 AM Tiffany Bakker CLIVE Owen, the film star, reveals why he was lured to the brilliant TV drama The Knick and his apprehension about intimate scenes with an actor. Changes ahead for The Bachelorette 0:00 AM Tiffany Dunk National TV Editor NOBODY expected The Bachelorette to be such a huge rating smash and Channel Ten is to cash in with a special episode and longer series next year. ’I bed three men in six episodes’ 0:00 AM Debbie Schipp National TV writer NICKI Wendt is pleased with her strike rate as the riotous former first lady on ABC’s The Ex-PM and admits it’s the most fun she has had on TV. Justin Bieber on dad, Jeremy Bieber’s awkward penis post October 20, 2015 11:27pm Hilarious ... Justin Bieber has defended his dad’s tweet boasting about the size of his penis.
